query:
with tenants(name) as (
          select unnest($1::text[])
        ),
        prefixes as (
          select name as prefix from tenants
          union all select 'recovery/' || name from tenants
        )
        select
            m.id as "id: Id",
            m.catalog_prefix,
            m.spec
        from prefixes p
        join storage_mappings m on starts_with(m.catalog_prefix, p.prefix);
